  "texts": [
    "This is particularly evident in the non-i.i.d. settings.",
    "Also, results suggest that federated TSK-FRBS and federated MLP-NN achieve comparable performance, within the context of the considered case study.As regards explainability, we have presented the results of the post-hoc explainability of MLP-NN and of the by-design interpretability of TSK-FRBS, also providing a comparative analysis of the two approaches.",
    "It turns out that the two approaches can lead to different local explanations, even if the underlying models achieve similar results in terms of regression metrics.",
    "A first major difference between the two approaches lies in their nature: the TSK-FRBS model provides insights about \"how\" an outcome is obtained, whereas the post-hoc method provides insight about \"why\" an outcome is provided.",
    "Consequently, a qualitative comparison is more reasonable than a quantitative one."
